        "authorId" : "92fc8a78-5aad-454c-9b1f-3b0641161b09",
        "body" : "OK, then let's give this a try with eccodes python and fortran. But then we could build the library in the same process. How do you get the tarballs created for the three different packages?\n",
        "createdAt" : "2016-06-09T15:01:26Z",
